sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Admin
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant DB as Database
    participant STORAGE as Supabase Storage
    participant M as Merchant

    Note over A,M: Admin Dashboard Overview

    A->>FE: Navigate to /admin/merchants
    FE->>DB: Query merchant statistics
    Note right of DB: Aggregate counts:<br/>- Total merchants<br/>- Pending verification<br/>- Verified merchants<br/>- Rejected merchants<br/>- Active subscriptions
    
    DB-->>FE: Return statistics
    
    FE->>A: Display merchant dashboard
    Note right of A: Summary cards:<br/>- Total: 1,247<br/>- Pending Review: 23<br/>- Verified: 1,180<br/>- Rejected: 44<br/>- Active Paid: 892
    
    FE->>DB: Query pending verification list
    Note right of DB: SELECT * FROM merchants<br/>WHERE verification_status = 'pending'<br/>ORDER BY verification_submitted_at ASC
    
    DB-->>FE: Return pending merchants
    
    FE->>A: Display pending review queue
    Note right of A: Table shows:<br/>- Merchant name<br/>- Submission date<br/>- Subscription tier<br/>- Days waiting<br/>- Quick actions
    
    Note over A,M: Review Merchant Documents
    
    A->>FE: Click merchant to review
    FE->>DB: Query merchant full profile
    Note right of DB: JOIN merchants<br/>WITH verification_documents<br/>WITH properties (if any)<br/>WITH audit_logs
    
    DB-->>FE: Return complete merchant data
    
    FE->>A: Display merchant review page
    Note right of A: Layout sections:<br/>1. Basic Info<br/>2. Documents<br/>3. Properties preview<br/>4. Verification history<br/>5. Approve/Reject actions
    
    A->>FE: View basic information
    FE->>A: Display merchant profile
    Note right of A: Shows:<br/>- Full name<br/>- Email, Phone<br/>- Business name<br/>- Registered date<br/>- Subscription tier<br/>- Trial status
    
    A->>FE: View uploaded documents
    FE->>DB: Query verification_documents
    Note right of DB: WHERE merchant_id<br/>AND document_type IN<br/>('ktp', 'npwp', 'property_deed')
    
    DB-->>FE: Return document URLs
    
    FE->>A: Display document viewer
    Note right of A: 3 tabs:<br/>1. KTP (ID Card)<br/>2. NPWP (Tax ID)<br/>3. Surat Properti (Deed)
    
    A->>FE: Click to enlarge document
    FE->>STORAGE: Fetch full-resolution image
    STORAGE-->>A: Display document in lightbox
    
    A->>A: Verify document authenticity
    Note right of A: Check:<br/>✓ Document clarity<br/>✓ Name matches profile<br/>✓ ID number format valid<br/>✓ Address readable<br/>✓ Not expired<br/>✓ No tampering signs
    
    A->>FE: View properties (if created)
    FE->>DB: Query properties WHERE merchant_id
    DB-->>FE: Return properties list
    
    FE->>A: Display properties preview
    Note right of A: Shows merchant's properties<br/>to verify legitimacy
    
    A->>FE: Check verification history
    FE->>DB: Query audit_logs WHERE merchant_id
    DB-->>FE: Return history
    
    FE->>A: Display timeline
    Note right of A: Shows:<br/>- Registration date<br/>- Document uploads<br/>- Previous rejections (if any)<br/>- Resubmissions
    
    Note over A,M: Approve Merchant Verification
    
    A->>FE: Click "Approve Verification"
    FE->>A: Show confirmation modal
    Note right of A: "Approve this merchant?<br/>This will:<br/>- Grant verified status<br/>- Enable auto-disbursement<br/>- Remove tenant limits<br/>- Full tier capacity"
    
    A->>FE: Add approval notes (optional)
    Note right of A: "Documents verified.<br/>Property deed confirmed."
    
    A->>FE: Confirm approval
    
    FE->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    
    DB->>DB: UPDATE merchants SET
    Note right of DB: verified: true,<br/>verification_status: 'approved',<br/>verified_at: NOW(),<br/>verified_by: admin_id
    
    DB->>DB: Remove non-verified restrictions
    Note right of DB: Before (Non-Verified):<br/>- max_tenants: 50% of tier<br/>- disbursement: manual (1-3 days)<br/>- max_pending: limited<br/><br/>After (Verified):<br/>- max_tenants: full tier limit<br/>- disbursement: auto (same day)<br/>- max_pending: unlimited
    
    DB->>DB: INSERT INTO merchant_verification_history
    Note right of DB: merchant_id, action: 'approved',<br/>performed_by: admin_id,<br/>approval_notes,<br/>timestamp
    
    DB->>DB: INSERT INTO notifications (merchant)
    Note right of DB: type: 'verification_approved',<br/>title: 'Account Verified!',<br/>message: 'Full features unlocked'
    
    DB->>DB: INSERT INTO audit_logs
    Note right of DB: entity_type: 'merchant',<br/>entity_id: merchant_id,<br/>action: 'verification_approved',<br/>performed_by: admin_id,<br/>ip_address, user_agent
    
    DB->>DB: Update platform metrics
    Note right of DB: verified_merchants_count++
    
    DB->>DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
    
    DB-->>M: Email: "Verification Approved!"
    Note right of M: Email content:<br/>Subject: Your SiHuni account is verified!<br/><br/>Body:<br/>- Congratulations message<br/>- Full features list<br/>- Auto-disbursement enabled<br/>- Full tenant capacity<br/>- Premium support access<br/>- Login button
    
    DB-->>M: Push notification: Verification approved
    
    DB-->>M: In-app banner: "Welcome to verified merchants!"
    
    FE->>A: Success toast: "Merchant approved"
    FE->>A: Move to next pending merchant
    
    Note over A,M: Reject Merchant Verification
    
    A->>FE: Click "Reject Verification"
    FE->>A: Show rejection form
    Note right of A: Required:<br/>- Rejection reason (dropdown)<br/>- Detailed explanation<br/>- Resubmission instructions
    
    A->>FE: Select rejection reason
    Note right of A: Predefined reasons:<br/>- Document unclear/blurry<br/>- Information mismatch<br/>- Expired documents<br/>- Invalid property deed<br/>- Suspicious activity<br/>- Incomplete submission<br/>- Other (specify)
    
    A->>FE: Write detailed explanation
    Note right of A: "KTP image is too blurry to verify.<br/>Please upload a clearer photo<br/>with good lighting."
    
    A->>FE: Add resubmission guidance
    Note right of A: "To resubmit:<br/>1. Take new photo in daylight<br/>2. Ensure all text is readable<br/>3. No shadows or glare<br/>4. Upload via Profile page"
    
    A->>FE: Confirm rejection
    
    FE->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    
    DB->>DB: UPDATE merchants SET
    Note right of DB: verification_status: 'rejected',<br/>rejected_at: NOW(),<br/>rejected_by: admin_id,<br/>rejection_reason: selected_reason,<br/>rejection_details: explanation,<br/>resubmission_instructions
    
    DB->>DB: Keep non-verified restrictions
    Note right of DB: Merchant continues with:<br/>- Limited tenant capacity<br/>- Manual disbursement<br/>- Restricted features
    
    DB->>DB: INSERT INTO merchant_verification_history
    Note right of DB: action: 'rejected',<br/>rejection_reason,<br/>performed_by: admin_id
    
    DB->>DB: INSERT INTO notifications (merchant)
    Note right of DB: type: 'verification_rejected',<br/>reason, details, instructions
    
    DB->>DB: INSERT INTO audit_logs
    Note right of DB: action: 'verification_rejected',<br/>reason, admin_id
    
    DB->>DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
    
    DB-->>M: Email: "Verification Rejected"
    Note right of M: Email content:<br/>Subject: Action Required - Verification Issue<br/><br/>Body:<br/>- Rejection reason<br/>- Detailed explanation<br/>- What to fix<br/>- How to resubmit<br/>- Support contact<br/>- Resubmit button
    
    DB-->>M: Push: Verification rejected - action required
    
    FE->>A: Success: "Rejection sent with instructions"
    FE->>A: Update pending count
    
    Note over A,M: Merchant Resubmission Review
    
    M->>FE: Fix issues + resubmit documents
    FE->>DB: UPDATE merchants SET
    Note right of DB: verification_status: 'pending',<br/>resubmission_count++,<br/>verification_submitted_at: NOW()
    
    DB-->>A: Notification: "Merchant resubmitted"
    
    A->>FE: View resubmission
    FE->>DB: Query verification history
    DB-->>FE: Return previous rejection + new submission
    
    FE->>A: Display resubmission review
    Note right of A: Shows:<br/>- Previous rejection reason<br/>- Admin who rejected<br/>- New documents<br/>- Resubmission count<br/>- Time since rejection
    
    A->>A: Compare old vs new documents
    A->>FE: Approve or reject again
    
    Note over A,M: Bulk Approval Actions
    
    A->>FE: Select multiple merchants (checkbox)
    Note right of A: Select merchants with<br/>similar issues or<br/>clearly valid docs
    
    A->>FE: Click "Bulk Approve"
    FE->>A: Show bulk confirmation
    Note right of A: "Approve 5 selected merchants?<br/>This action cannot be undone."
    
    A->>FE: Confirm bulk approval
    
    FE->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    
    loop For each selected merchant
        DB->>DB: UPDATE merchants SET verified = true
        DB->>DB: INSERT audit_logs
        DB->>DB: INSERT notifications
        DB-->>M: Send approval emails
    end
    
    DB->>DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
    
    FE->>A: Success: "5 merchants approved"
    
    Note over A,M: Search & Filter Merchants
    
    A->>FE: Use search bar
    Note right of A: Search by:<br/>- Name<br/>- Email<br/>- Phone<br/>- Business name
    
    FE->>DB: Query merchants WHERE
    Note right of DB: full_name ILIKE '%search%'<br/>OR email ILIKE '%search%'<br/>OR business_name ILIKE '%search%'
    
    DB-->>FE: Return matching merchants
    
    A->>FE: Apply filters
    Note right of A: Filters:<br/>- Status (verified/pending/rejected)<br/>- Subscription tier<br/>- Registration date range<br/>- Properties count<br/>- Tenant count
    
    FE->>DB: Complex query with filters
    DB-->>FE: Return filtered results
    
    Note over A,M: View Merchant Analytics
    
    A->>FE: Click merchant for detailed view
    FE->>DB: Query merchant analytics
    
    DB->>DB: Aggregate merchant data
    Note right of DB: Calculate:<br/>- Total revenue collected<br/>- Total tenants<br/>- Properties & units<br/>- Payment collection rate<br/>- Active contracts<br/>- Subscription value (MRR)
    
    DB-->>FE: Return analytics
    
    FE->>A: Display merchant profile page
    Note right of A: Tabs:<br/>1. Overview (stats)<br/>2. Properties<br/>3. Tenants<br/>4. Transactions<br/>5. Verification docs<br/>6. Activity logs<br/>7. Actions
    
    A->>FE: View activity logs tab
    FE->>DB: Query audit_logs
    DB-->>FE: Return merchant activities
    
    FE->>A: Display activity timeline
    Note right of A: Shows:<br/>- Login history<br/>- Property changes<br/>- Tenant additions<br/>- Payment activities<br/>- Settings changes